b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1187,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding an Issue with the Amount of Rupies Required to Craft Certain Void Weapons","message":"<div>We have confirmed an issue where more than the intended amount of rupies are expended for certain Void weapons when using Craft, Enhance, or Dismantle under Crafting.<\/div><div>This issue was resolved in a data update at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1585634400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Starting around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1585639800\\"><\/span>, we will send all players who crafted affected weapons the difference between the rupies spent and the rupies that should have been required.<\/div><div>\\u30fbIf a player used materials obtained from the Cerulean Ghost, Lambent Ghost, or Violet Ghost to craft a tier two or tier three weapon directly from the tree, this will also apply to the amount of rupies consumed when crafting the tier one or tier two weapons.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe gift will be sent to the goodie boxes of affected players.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Affected Weapons and Details<\/div><div>1. Tier one weapons crafted using materials obtained from the Blazing Ghost, Cerulean Ghost, Lambent Ghost, or Violet Ghost<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity\/Type\/Attunement)<\/div><div>\\u30fbRest Eternal (3\\u2605\/blade\/unattuned)<\/div><div>\\u30fbHeartseeker (3\\u2605\/lance\/unattuned)<\/div><div>\\u30fbMockery (3\\u2605\/bow\/unattuned)<\/div><div>\\u30fbClamor Wand (3\\u2605\/wand\/unattuned)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Rupies Consumed when Crafted<\/div><div>Incorrect: 3,000 rupies<\/div><div>Correct: 1,000 rupies<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Rupies Consumed when Dismantled<\/div><div>Incorrect: 6,000 rupies<\/div><div>Correct: 2,000 rupies<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>2. Tier two weapons crafted using materials obtained from the Blazing Ghost<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity\/Type\/Attunement)<\/div><div>\\u30fbResentment (3\\u2605\/blade\/shadow)<\/div><div>\\u30fbQuavering Bloodlust (3\\u2605\/lance\/shadow)<\/div><div>\\u30fbCacklemurk (3\\u2605\/bow\/shadow)<\/div><div>\\u30fbWickedheart (3\\u2605\/wand\/shadow)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Rupies Consumed when Enhanced<\/div><div>Incorrect: 15,000 rupies<\/div><div>Correct: 5,000 rupies<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Rupies Consumed when Dismantled<\/div><div>Incorrect: 30,000 rupies<\/div><div>Correct: 10,000 rupies<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>3. Tier three weapons crafted using materials obtained from the Blazing Ghost<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity\/Type\/Attunement)<\/div><div>\\u30fbUnwelcome Meeting (4\\u2605\/blade\/shadow)<\/div><div>\\u30fbSpear of Tragedy (4\\u2605\/lance\/shadow)<\/div><div>\\u30fbHowlshadow (4\\u2605\/bow\/shadow)<\/div><div>\\u30fbDarkheart (4\\u2605\/wand\/shadow)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Rupies Consumed when Enhanced<\/div><div>Incorrect: 90,000 rupies<\/div><div>Correct: 30,000 rupies<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Rupies Consumed when Dismantled<\/div><div>Incorrect: 180,000 rupies<\/div><div>Correct: 60,000 rupies<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div>","start_time":1585634400,"prev_article_id":"1196","next_article_id":"1189","image_path":"","update_time":1585216347}}}'